Death and the Maiden;;81;;82;;R;;Paulina Escobar (Sigourney Weaver) is convinced that the guest (Ben Kingsley) her lawyer husband (Stuart Wilson) brings home is the same man who who kidnapped, tortured and raped her years ago. Holding him captive at gunpoint, she repeatedly attacks him and demands that he confess his crime. Her husband tries to stand by his wife and her claims, but he begins to doubt her story and the claims. She forces her husband to represent the guest in a mock trial that she devises.;;Drama;;Roman Polanski;;1994;;Sigourney Weaver,Ben Kingsley,Stuart Wilson,Karen Strassman,Carlos Moreno,Krystia Mova,Ariel Dorfman,Rafael Yglesias;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_and_the_maiden